This is houston's fifth ward.

01:22.500 --> 01:26.200
It accounts for a large percent
of the city's growing homicide rate,

01:25.600 --> 01:29.100
Due to gang violence
And a bustling narcotics trade.

01:29.300 --> 01:31.300
Although in the last 48 hours,

01:31.300 --> 01:34.500
There have been
3 distinctive murders in the ward.

01:34.700 --> 01:35.600
Distinctive ? 

01:35.600 --> 01:38.600
3 men, 3 different
socioeconomic groups,

01:38.600 --> 01:41.000
