The ward's detectives
are inundated with homicides.

02:01.200 --> 02:03.500
Gang violence is a big problem.

02:04.100 --> 02:05.400
Shootings,

02:05.400 --> 02:07.000
Armed robberies,
it's an everyday occurrence,

02:07.000 --> 02:08.800
But this type
of street attack

02:08.800 --> 02:09.800
Is new to them.

02:10.100 --> 02:11.600
Could it be gang related,

02:11.600 --> 02:13.700
Maybe some new type
of initiation rite ? 

02:14.100 --> 02:16.200
The gangs in the ward use guns.

02:16.500 --> 02:19.400
In fact, no known gangs
exhibit this type of m.O.

02:19.400 --> 02:20.300
What about dope ? 

02:20.700 --> 02:22.200
These guys come up with
pretty freaky ways

02:22.200 --> 02:24.100
Of killing the competition
to get their message out.

02:24.400 --> 02:27.100
Yeah, but there just
doesn't seem to be any connection

02:27.100 --> 02:29.100
Between the victims
and the drug world.

02:29.300 --> 02:30.300
Homeless man,

02:30.300 --> 02:31.700
A construction worker...

02:33.100 --> 02:34.400
Security guard.

02:34.600 --> 02:37.000
Just 3 dead men and no witnesses.

02:37.000 --> 02:39.100
We're looking for
a homicidal serial criminal

02:39.100 --> 02:40.400
In a neighborhood
populated by criminals.

02:40.400 --> 02:42.400
The challenge will be
separating him from the rest.

02:42.600 --> 02:45.800
We have no evidence, no apparent
interaction between the unsub

02:45.800 --> 02:47.400
And the victims
pre- Or postmortem,

02:47.400 --> 02:49.500
And an indistinguishable M.O.

02:49.700 --> 02:50.800
Should be simple.

03:07.400 --> 03:10.000
"Criminal minds" 217

03:39.400 --> 03:41.600
"our life is made
by the death of others."

03:42.400 --> 03:43.600
Leonardo Da Vinci.

03:44.500 --> 03:45.800
We got a construction worker...

03:46.700 --> 03:47.900
Outsider in the community.

03:48.800 --> 03:50.000
We got a security guard...

03:50.200 --> 03:51.200
That's an authority figure.

03:51.200 --> 03:52.200
And then we got a homeless man.

03:53.100 --> 03:54.700
That's a powerless victim
that no one would notice missing.

03:54.700 --> 03:55.800
So who's he targeting ? 

03:56.500 --> 03:59.600
Let's see if any of the victims
frequented the same stores or sites.

04:00.000 --> 04:01.500
He used blitz attacks,

