victims into coming close.

04:06.300 --> 04:08.100
And he also used
the element of surprise,

04:08.100 --> 04:10.700
Which means he may have stalked
his victims prior to killing them.

04:11.000 --> 04:12.900
Well, if that's the case,
i want to go to the last crime scene

04:12.900 --> 04:14.300
