he may have been hiding.

04:14.300 --> 04:15.800
I want to see
the neighborhood for myself.

04:15.800 --> 04:16.800
Good.
I'll go with you.

04:16.800 --> 04:18.600
The rest of us will go to
the precinct and set up shop.

04:19.100 --> 04:21.399
I'll map out the area
and see if i can find any places

04:21.399 --> 04:23.100
The victims would have
visited in the neighborhood.

04:23.100 --> 04:25.800
Good. Maybe we can find
a connection between them.
I'll help you with that.

04:25.800 --> 04:26.700
I can handle it.

04:28.100 --> 04:29.500
