Reid. Prentiss will help you
with the geographical profiling

04:34.700 --> 04:35.700
And victimology.

04:36.200 --> 04:37.000
Fine.

04:44.300 --> 04:45.900
Remember, this is a high-Crime area.

04:46.100 --> 04:48.100
Be vigilant.
Nobody goes anywhere alone.

05:27.500 --> 05:28.600
FBI, right ? 

