07:00.100 --> 07:00.900
What murder ? 

07:01.300 --> 07:02.500
Security guard.

07:02.500 --> 07:03.500
Oh, my god.

07:03.500 --> 07:05.200
No. No.
He chased us,

07:05.400 --> 07:07.300
