I swear, i ain't touch him.

07:07.300 --> 07:08.600
Don't say another word, Kelvin.

07:08.800 --> 07:12.400
Kelvin... I only have one question
for you and then you can go.

07:12.900 --> 07:15.100
Did the security guard
fire his weapon at you ? 

07:15.300 --> 07:18.200
No. He, like,
shot into the air to scare us.

07:18.200 --> 07:19.200
