Yeah, we're on it.

09:08.600 --> 09:10.800
Unless...
you ok with that, Reid ? 

09:11.700 --> 09:12.500
I'm fine with that.

09:14.500 --> 09:17.200
We should check to see if there are
any mental hospitals in the area,

09:17.200 --> 09:19.100
Maybe someone who was recently
released into the streets.

09:19.100 --> 09:20.100
Mm-Hmm. Got it.

09:20.100 --> 09:22.400
Morgan, can you cover
the police records for the last week ? 

09:22.400 --> 09:24.300
If it's someone
who's been recently made homeless,

09:24.300 --> 09:27.200
