comfort items, blankets,

09:27.200 --> 09:29.500
Toiletries... We might be able
to track a pattern of theft.

09:29.500 --> 09:30.700
Thanks.
Done.

09:45.800 --> 09:48.000
Are you lonely
in the lone star state ? 

09:48.400 --> 09:49.500
Are you wearing chaps ? 

