Only in your dreams, Garcia.

09:52.200 --> 09:54.100
Oh, not necessarily.

09:54.400 --> 09:55.500
I have photoshop.

09:55.800 --> 09:57.000
Hey, hey, behave.

09:57.600 --> 09:59.900
Focus your little
twisted mind for me, ok ? 

10:00.400 --> 10:02.100
I need police records
from the fifth ward...

10:02.100 --> 10:03.800
Small thefts and burglaries.
Can you do that ? 

10:04.100 --> 10:05.900
Aren't you at that
very station right now.

10:05.900 --> 10:07.500
Yeah, but it's a small precinct

10:07.500 --> 10:09.300
And these guys are stretched. Trust me.

10:09.600 --> 10:10.400
Got it.

10:11.100 --> 10:11.900
Oh, Garcia.

10:12.300 --> 10:15.500
See if you can find before and after
pictures of demolitions in the area.

10:15.500 --> 10:18.200
Maybe we can nail down a building where
the unsub may have worked or lived in.

10:18.400 --> 10:19.500
How far back ? 

10:19.900 --> 10:20.800
A week.

10:23.000 --> 10:23.700
And Garcia...

10:24.200 --> 10:26.500
I better not ever find
any photoshop pictures of me...

10:26.500 --> 10:28.600
Oh, trust me, my vision.

10:29.200 --> 10:30.600
You will never find them.

11:11.800 --> 11:12.700
Get out ! 

11:43.700 --> 11:45.800
Victim's name is Travis Overby.

11:46.000 --> 11:47.200
That's his buddy over there.

11:47.200 --> 11:49.500
He was working
a jackhammer on a new trunkline.

11:50.200 --> 11:52.600
He said one second
travis was going down the sewer,

11:52.600 --> 11:54.900
The next second
he was down at the bottom dead.

11:55.300 --> 11:56.800
From one second to the next.

12:01.100 --> 12:02.200
Someone has to go down.

12:02.900 --> 12:04.200
Aw, see, this ain't cool.

12:11.300 --> 12:12.700
I'm putting in for hazard pay.

12:13.400 --> 12:14.300
Good luck with that.

12:40.200 --> 12:41.900
It's pretty clean for a sewer ! 

