What do you mean,
what's the matter with me ? 

15:45.900 --> 15:47.700
I have never seen you act like this.

15:48.300 --> 15:50.000
Oh, really ?  Oh, in the months
that you know me,

15:50.000 --> 15:51.200
You've never seen me
act this way ? 

15:51.200 --> 15:52.600
Hey, no offense,
Emily, but...

15:53.000 --> 15:54.700
You don't really know what
you're talking about, do you ? 

15:59.800 --> 16:01.100
Good. Thanks.

16:01.300 --> 16:02.300
Just got back from
the local homeless shelter.

16:02.300 --> 16:05.100
The administrator hasn't noticed anyone
new displaying aggressive behavior.

16:05.100 --> 16:06.200
He's not in
a homeless shelter.

16:06.200 --> 16:07.300
I just talked
to Gideon and Morgan.

16:07.300 --> 16:08.400
They think that he's killing

16:08.400 --> 16:10.200
To protect some makeshift
shelter of his own.

16:10.200 --> 16:11.400
So are we ready
for a profile yet ? 

16:11.700 --> 16:12.700
We're missing something.

16:13.300 --> 16:15.500
How did this homeless man
learn to kill so efficiently ? 

16:15.700 --> 16:16.500
You know what we need ? 

16:16.900 --> 16:17.800
We need to get lucky.

16:18.100 --> 16:19.400
We need him to make a mistake.

16:35.200 --> 16:36.000
Hey.

16:37.700 --> 16:39.000
Come on, man, get out of there ! 

16:41.400 --> 16:42.700
I see you right there ! 

16:44.100 --> 16:45.300
Iaqui tengo mi tienda ! 

16:45.300 --> 16:47.100
There's a shelter
a couple of blocks from here.

16:56.200 --> 16:57.300
Vayase...

17:00.800 --> 17:02.100
Papa ! 

17:20.000 --> 17:21.200
Please help my daddy ! 

17:21.500 --> 17:23.099
I need help !  I was attacked ! 

17:23.500 --> 17:24.800
Can i get some help here, please ? 

17:24.800 --> 17:28.400
Please... Call my house
to come get my daughter. Please.

17:29.800 --> 17:30.600
Maria...

17:34.900 --> 17:36.800
Is my papa gonna be ok ? 

17:37.400 --> 17:38.200
Yes.

17:41.700 --> 17:45.000
Maria, could you answer
a few questions for us ? 

17:45.300 --> 17:47.300
It would really help us
find the bad guy.

17:51.200 --> 17:53.900
Did he say anything
to your papa ? 

17:54.800 --> 17:55.700
No.

17:59.100 --> 18:01.800
What were you and your papa
doing before the bad guy came ? 

18:06.900 --> 18:08.700
Papa took out the garbage.

18:10.200 --> 18:11.900
And then he jumped out...

18:12.700 --> 18:14.200
And he hit my papa.

18:17.700 --> 18:19.000
I was screaming at him.

18:19.000 --> 18:20.900
Don't hurt my papa ! 

18:21.900 --> 18:23.700
I thought he was gonna
hit me, too.

